Mapping & Ideas by: kamikaze|deadeye`

Cannon by: #NeutraLized



This is the second release.


_________
|*Fixed*|
-----------

-There was an issue with people getting stuck in teleports due to heavy player loads; This has been fixed and should no longer be a problem.

-An area where CT's had a BIG advantage has been modified to even out the game play, zombies should have a good chance now.

-An elevator has been upgraded with doors so you can no longer be shot off.

-1 room has been totally re-done to add to the game play.

-More props have been added to provide better barricades.

-The spawn has been split into two areas to help disperse people around the map.



Mapping & Ideas by: kamikaze|deadeye`

Cannon by: #NeutraLized
